{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"769abece99","title":"一军团主力暂在现地待机","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1c566c0e80","index":0,"year":1936,"month":9,"day":18,"articleId":"769abece99"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ed3dc0e420","type":"paragraph","text":"一军团主力暂在现地待机！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"769abece99"},{"id":"eff3ae2097","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年9月18日）彭司令员：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"769abece99"},{"id":"aa09387658","type":"paragraph","text":"两次电达朱张，要其速占界石铺，尚未得复。打击胡军，须以四方面军为主力，在其部署与决心未明之前，一军团主力暂时宜在现地待机。如能在固原北部再给何柱国一个打击，使后路无被切断之虞则更稳妥。将来进攻宁夏，一方面军只能从盐池、豫旺、同心城分路前进，而以同心城以西划为四方面军之作战线，故后路保持甚为重要。请的行","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"769abece99"},{"id":"3eb3e64d53","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"769abece99"},{"id":"874ef6eaee","type":"paragraph","text":"十八日二十时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"769abece99"},{"id":"b9048bff9a","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给红军第一方面军司令员、西方野战军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"769abece99"},{"id":"2de59f2f55","type":"paragraph","text":"12]指1936年9月15日毛泽东、周恩来、彭德怀，17日12时毛泽东、周恩来给朱德、张国秦的电报。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"769abece99"},{"id":"6d975c6a06","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]胡，指胡宗南，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第一军军长兼第一师师长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"769abece99"},{"id":"026566527a","type":"paragraph","text":"[41何柱国，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部骑兵军军长。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"769abece99"}],"page":{"id":"e489ad2ffa","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"769abece99","start":147,"end":147}}}},"__N_SSG":true}